{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822980/extras/desc_graphic_1.png?t=1737449892\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LOCKED IN A FIRE TOWER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A [HOST] challenges you to a deadly game of chance where a <strong><i>forest fire</i></strong> spreads with each flip of a card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose where the fire spreads, but only on <i><strong>your</strong></i> side of the field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>The more turns you take, the closer the fire gets.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822980/extras/gif1.gif?t=1737449892\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A GAME OF CHANCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some cards have a chance to deliver a <i><strong>random utility</strong></i>, or force you to <i><strong>take another turn</strong></i>. Choose wisely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822980/extras/gif2.gif?t=1737449892\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE UTILITIES TO OUTWIT THE [HOST]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each Utility has unique way of <strong><i>skewing the odds of the game.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use their various effects to your advantage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822980/extras/gif3.gif?t=1737449892\" />\t</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A ZERO-SUM GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every card type has a <strong><i>fixed amount</i></strong>. Count them to make the best decision possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But count carefully, <strong><i>the [HOST] is keeping track as well</i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How well does your memory stack up?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" sr